  <p>“Absolute power corrupts absolutely.”</p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>“Who shall watch the watchmen themselves (Quis custodiet ipsos custodes?)                  <br />
 “Diamond me no diamonds, prize me no prizes…” Alfred, Lord Tennyson</p>
</blockquote>

