  <p>Sometimes I need what only you can provide - your absence.</p>
</blockquote>

<blockquote>
  <p>“If you trust in yourself. . .and believe in your dreams. . .and follow your star. . . you’ll still get beaten by people who spent their time working hard and learning things and weren’t so lazy”</p>
